{"tid":277581,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"IDC：2021年Windows phone業務將下降至0%","createTime":"2017-06-09T17:01:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T15:02:21.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9142888c9f6144a2300f3a995e73289fdd5ff5f","tid":277581,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T17:01:07.000Z","msg":"2017/06/09 22:26<br />\n市場調研機構IDC日前發佈最新報告稱，2021年Windows phone在全球市場中的比重將下降到0%。今年微軟驍龍相比較去年降幅達到了80.9%。<br />\n<br />\nIDC在報告中稱，微軟在2017年的銷量大約為110萬台，相比較去年同期下降80.9%。而且這種情況到目前依然沒有改觀的跡象，而寓意厚望的Surface Phone要推遲到今年年底明年年初的時候發佈。<br />\n<br />\nIDC專家表示：「由於缺乏新的硬件合作夥伴、開發者支持，Windows Phone出貨量將會繼續下滑，而且整個平台沒有任何立即復蘇的徵兆。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然IDC在給微軟潑冷水，但是微軟並沒有放棄Windows Phone業務。近日有消息顯示，微軟正在內部進行相關係統以及硬件的測試。這款機將會採用不同的Windows Mobile分支，以期獲得更好的體驗。微軟希望這款明年推出的新系統能夠給用戶以不一樣的體驗，但是微軟標誌性的動態瓷貼並不會被放棄，畢竟這是微軟之前與蘋果和谷歌競爭的一大賣點。消息源方面暫時還沒有新機發佈日期的消息，但消息人士猜測最終產品可能要等上大約一年才能完成。<br />\n<br />\n根據長期跟蹤微軟動態的Mary Jo Foley表示，微軟投資者關係總監Chris Suh已經告訴她，目前業務帶來的收入基本為零。報告顯示，截止到2017年1月份的前3個月，美國地區Windows Phone佔有份額是1.6%，相比去年同期的2.5%再一次出現了下滑的狀況。"},{"pid":"9451fbc1029994b69bcc86407818241652ce0aec","tid":277581,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T18:28:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d54da8c76a869add94a28156c33c2032b8dded84","tid":277581,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T19:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3571ba804420bcd9c1031359a9072cb13d2c6c2d","tid":277581,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T06:38:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">但是微軟標誌性的動態瓷貼並不會被放棄</span>本來有少少其望，見到呢句心都死埋"},{"pid":"1db39fd8614af75548a6a58622d53ec751135e35","tid":277581,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T08:04:16.000Z","msg":"以前成個xda都係hd2, <br />\n大把homemade apps, playstation, winXP, linux都裝得落<br />\n仆街M$係都要孤兒晒啲舊機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b0995d932f7a5f97e4ec365f0b9b06bc3a606b9","tid":277581,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T09:11:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"588c7bcaa9de60b773ed97e33d1996ca40bca490","tid":277581,"uid":52311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T09:26:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">但是微軟標誌性的動態瓷貼並不會被放棄</span>本來有少少其望，見到呢句心都死埋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n跌到0主因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n出部s835既機3000蚊可以dual boot android 送多部xbox one加一年office 365 應該會多d人買既"},{"pid":"99cb483cfcb84bb5c8da04719cd1e520e931b255","tid":277581,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T14:45:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當日啲誠意呢"},{"pid":"2fd54e8cc478541a5160f23372957393e7d6d6ed","tid":277581,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:02:21.000Z","msg":"2012 IDC:<br />\n2016 window phone市佔超iOS <br />\n<a href=\"http://iphone.appleinsider.com/articles/12/06/06/idc_projects_windows_phone_to_surpass_apples_iphone_by_2016.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fiphone.appleinsider.com%2Farticles%2F12%2F06%2F06%2Fidc_projects_windows_phone_to_surpass_apples_iphone_by_2016.html&d=xgRtEjYHviJHkv2SvKNv3f1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=1b30d4ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://iphone.appleinsider.com/articles/12/06/06/idc_projects_windows_phone_to_surpass_apples_iphone_by_2016.html</a>"}]}